# CloudPilot Redesign v3: ai-sdk.dev Inspired (Minimal, Developer-Focused)

## Objective
Redesign cloudpilot-site based on ai-sdk.dev's elegant, minimal design aesthetic focusing on clarity, pragmatism, and developer values.

## ai-sdk.dev Design Pattern Analysis

### Key Characteristics
1. **Minimal, Clean Aesthetic** - Generous whitespace, no clutter
2. **Neutral Palette** - Black, white, grays only (no bright colors)
3. **System Fonts** - Geist (sans-serif), Source Serif 4 (serif accents)
4. **Pragmatic Clarity** - Focus on technical authenticity, no marketing fluff
5. **Developer Values** - Transparency, pragmatism, authenticity
6. **Visual + Text Pairings** - Feature sections balance code with description
7. **Social Proof via Community** - Developer testimonials (authentic voices)
8. **Persistent Clean Header** - Simple navigation, no clutter
9. **Dark/Light Mode** - Respects user preferences
10. **Micro-interactions** - Subtle, purposeful animations

### Color System (ai-sdk.dev Inspired)
- **Light Mode**: White (#ffffff) background, black (#000000) text
- **Dark Mode**: Very dark gray (#0f1117) background, light text (#e6edf3)
- **Accents**: Minimal - maybe one accent color for CTAs (#0066cc or similar)
- **No Gradients**: Pure, simple colors only

### Typography
- **Headlines**: Inter or system font, bold, large but readable
- **Body**: System fonts (Inter/Arial), clear hierarchy
- **Code**: Monospace for technical content (if needed)
- **No Excessive Sizing**: Readable at all sizes

### Layout Patterns
- **Hero**: Simple headline, subheadline, CTA - minimal design
- **Features**: Left-aligned image/visual, right-aligned text (or vice versa)
- **Navigation**: Persistent header, simple links, no mega-menus
- **Testimonials**: Developer quotes, real names/companies
- **CTA**: Simple button with clear intent
- **Whitespace**: Generous, intentional spacing

## Implementation Tasks

### WAVE 1: Foundation
- [ ] Update CSS: Light/dark mode support
- [ ] Remove all gradients, shadows (minimal design)
- [ ] Update colors to neutral palette (black/white/gray)
- [ ] Switch font to system fonts (Inter or Geist if available)
- [ ] Remove animations (keep minimal micro-interactions only)

### WAVE 2: Header & Hero
- [ ] Redesign Navbar: Clean, minimal, simple links
- [ ] Redesign Hero: Simple headline, subheadline, basic CTA
- [ ] Remove all visual effects, gradients

### WAVE 3: Feature Sections
- [ ] Features: Left/right text + visual alternating
- [ ] HowItWorks: Simple numbered steps, text-focused
- [ ] About: Honest, transparent messaging
- [ ] Remove all cards, borders (flat design)

### WAVE 4: Social Proof & CTA
- [ ] Testimonials: Real developer quotes, simple layout
- [ ] Social Proof: Honest, community-focused
- [ ] CTA: Clear, simple call to action

### WAVE 5: Polish & Testing
- [ ] Dark/light mode toggle (if possible)
- [ ] Minimal micro-interactions (hover effects only)
- [ ] Responsive design verification
- [ ] Performance check
- [ ] Final visual audit

## Success Criteria
✓ Minimal, clean, no unnecessary decoration
✓ Neutral palette only (black, white, grays)
✓ Developer-focused messaging
✓ Clear typography hierarchy
✓ Generous whitespace
✓ Technical authenticity feel
✓ Simple, persistent navigation
✓ Community-focused testimonials
✓ No gradients or fancy effects
✓ Fast load, minimal CSS

Status: PLANNING
